## Account Purpose Definition

### Domain-Based Account

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| **Account Strategy** | Domain-based Multi-Account |
| **Domain** | {{ account_domain }} |
| **Description** | {{ account_description }} |

### Account Structure

This account represents the **{{ account_domain }}** domain. The account structure will be:

```
{{ account_domain }} Account
├── Development databases/schemas (Data Product workflow)
├── Test databases/schemas (Data Product workflow)
└── Production databases/schemas (Data Product workflow)
```

