Based on your Platform Foundation naming conventions:

{%- if account_name_prefix | upper != "NONE" %}
`{{ account_name_prefix | lower }}_{{ account_domain | lower }}`
{%- else %}
`{{ account_domain | lower }}`
{%- endif %}

